nce for an hybrid formation scenario\nfor the first time in an $N$-body, hydrodynamical, cosmological ``zoom-in''\nsimulation. Furthermore, we also identify a nuclear stellar ring in the\nsimulation, with properties similar to those of the Milky Way's nuclear stellar\ndisc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Mar 2023 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-24"}
