els used in IdP_FSD. Extensive experiments show that the proposed IdP_FSD\nnot only achieves high detection performance on different benchmark datasets\nand image qualities but also raises the bar for manipulators to evade the\ndetection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2023 09:33:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-24"}
